title: Jẹ iwifunni - Orbital Temple
heading: Ṣe iwifunni Nigbati O Dide
description:
Ni Oṣu kọkanla ọjọ 28, Ọdun 2025, Tẹmpili Orbital yoo goke.
Fi imeeli rẹ silẹ, ati pe a yoo sọ fun ọ nigbati o ba de aaye.

form.successMessage: A yoo de ọdọ rẹ nigbati o ba goke.
form.errorMessage: Nkankan ti ko tọ. Jọwọ gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.
